<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" type="notes">
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="20997">Notes</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="20997">
The description of 
<taxonomicName class="Polychaeta" family="Polynoidae" genus="Harmothoe" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Harmothoe longisetis" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="longisetis">Harmothoe longisetis</taxonomicName>
of 
<bibRefCitation author="Fauvel, P." journalOrPublisher="Paul Lechevalier, Paris" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" title="Faune de France: Polychetes errantes" year="1923">Fauvel (1923)</bibRefCitation>
partly refers to 
<taxonomicName class="Polychaeta" family="Polynoidae" genus="Harmothoe" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Harmothoe glabra" order="Phyllodocida" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" phylum="Annelida" rank="species" species="glabra">Harmothoe glabra</taxonomicName>
(Malmgren, 1866) (
<bibRefCitation author="Barnich, R" journalOrPublisher="Abhandlungen der Senckenbergischen Naturforschenden Gesellschaft" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" pagination="1 - 167" title="The Aphroditoidea (Annelida: Polychaeta) of the Mediterranean Sea" volume="599" year="2003">Barnich and Fiege 2003</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="Barnich, Ruth" journalOrPublisher="Zootaxa" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" pagination="1 - 76" title="Revision of the genus Harmothoe Kinberg, 1865 (Polychaeta: Polynoidae) in the Northeast Atlantic" volume="2104" year="2009">Barnich and Fiege 2009</bibRefCitation>
). Thus, records identified using Fauvel's key could belong to either species. Recent records (e.g. 
<bibRefCitation author="Chatzigeorgiou, G" journalOrPublisher="Hellenic Centre for Marine Research" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" title="Polychaetes from two subtidal rocky shores of the North coast of Crete, collected for the NaGISA project 2007 - 2008." year="2016">Chatzigeorgiou et al. 2016</bibRefCitation>
) were identified using the key and descriptions by 
<bibRefCitation author="Barnich, R" journalOrPublisher="Abhandlungen der Senckenbergischen Naturforschenden Gesellschaft" pageId="0" pageNumber="20997" pagination="1 - 167" title="The Aphroditoidea (Annelida: Polychaeta) of the Mediterranean Sea" volume="599" year="2003">Barnich and Fiege (2003)</bibRefCitation>
. Type locality: Mediterranean (Adriatic).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
